RT @martinepowers: What happens after FDA says ‘yes’ to the first coronavirus vaccine?

On today’s Post Reports, we dive deep into vaccine distribution. We talked to @Pfizer, @DHLUS, @Walgreens, the Maine CDC…

And… we talked to The Dry Ice Guy.
